data.description: Come take a look at this 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home in a great cul-de-sac location and near I-75 via Wade Green, as well as the Hickory Grove entrance to the Express Lanes. This home features impressive improvements, including new Hardi Plank siding, new roof with GAF 30 year shingles, new gutters, owner's bath remodel, new kitchen counters and backsplash, new garage doors (tracks and openers too), updated flooring in upstairs secondary bath, and much more. You'll love the space in this home from the moment you walk through the front door into the two story foyer and curved staircase before you. The open concept family room and kitchen are at the rear of the home, while the large dining space can accommodate all your family gatherings. In front of the dining room is flex/bonus space that can be used however you see fit. Upstairs you'll find a spacious owner's retreat with a gorgeous bay window that's screaming to be a reading nook, updated ensuite bathroom with an oversized shower and large walk-in closet. The two secondary bedrooms upstairs conveniently share a jack and jill bathroom. The backyard is fully fenced and ready for your kids and pets to roam freely! The seller will also provide a Home Warranty for one year from date of purchase. This is the home you've been waiting for. Call today for your showing!
